Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:03.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1125,930)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒醒  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今天得搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're moving today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.87,0:01:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.58,0:01:07.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:07.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're leaving home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会变成乡巴佬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to become peasants
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.55,0:01:11.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没吃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:11.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more food
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.17,0:01:12.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:12.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.96,0:01:15.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乡巴佬只吃捣碎的蚌壳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:15.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peasants only eat mashed-up clamshells
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April fools
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.14,0:01:25.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:25.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好渴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在渴到极点了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is an extreme thirst
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.95,0:01:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好累
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要把饮料全喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure can't wait to drink all these drinks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April fools
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是在高兴个什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's he so happy about?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四月一号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April 1st?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630.877,360)}四月一日
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.47,0:02:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节是海绵宝宝最喜欢的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April fools' day is SpongeBob's favorite holiday
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我今天不能来上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I can't come in today
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感染上了很严重的病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught something terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感染了什么病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd you catch?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到了今天的日历
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught sight of the calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(520.725,920)}感 染
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边有个人要见你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's someone here to see you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说他是从藤壶湾艺术馆来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Says he's from the barnacle bay art museum
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想给你本月最佳艺术家称号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he wants to honor you as artist of the month
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.25,0:02:34.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:34.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.80,0:02:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,艺术商在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the art dealer?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚错过他了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just missed him
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  不过他要我们转告你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he told us to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转告我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me what?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要我转告你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He told me to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April Fool
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴一直以来在这上班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's been nice working here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的照顾  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把最后一笔工资寄到我信箱  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just send my last check to the P.O. Box, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  刚刚那是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, it was just a joke
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天不会再开你玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more jokes on you today
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.75,0:03:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有不少其他人愿意被开玩笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's lots of other willing participants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要不开我玩笑就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as it's not me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能请你告诉我叉子在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me where the forks are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(592.825,274)}餐具
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在这  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're right here, lady
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这是勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this is a spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April Fools
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(965.343,160)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要什么服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How may I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来两份大号薯条跟一份巨无霸蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me two large fries and a jumbo krabby patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.75,0:03:53.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:53.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那位哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd that other guy go?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April fools
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm right here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太逗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was pretty good
