Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚要我在饮料里加两块冰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You asked for a couple of ice cubes in your drink
