Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我听不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.28,0:10:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我问心无愧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My conscience is clear
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是感人的好事才能让他哭成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must have been pretty good to make him cry like that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.37,0:10:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐  混球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April fools, jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这个混球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stink
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.79,0:10:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我承认  我很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I admit it, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无意伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to hurt you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢住在你隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like living next door
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你早上特别吵的雾角闹钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like your foghorn alarm in the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你晚上的尖笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your high-pitched giggling at night
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢小蜗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I also like Gary, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟所有我迫不得已接触到的其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all of the other people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm forced to be in contact with
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  全都是真心话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, is all that true?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  全是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all true
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连利马豆跟追车都是真心话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even the part about the lima beans and the car chase?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对  随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是你一定要跟我保证不跟别人说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you have to promise not to tell anybody
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April fools
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April fools
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.01,0:11:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,April fools
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚骗了你们所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just fooled you all
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了章鱼哥我们要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would we do without Squidward?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.94,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,313)}海神黄金锅铲
