Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:58.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1094.478,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(438.609,712)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(406.564,300)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(264.367,304)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(406.565,628)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(396.551,422)}客串
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(1031.434,676)}配音  海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1033.23,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1119.557,496)}厨师博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:09.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710.989,382)}油脂硬汉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1077.499,878)}叉子
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请看那终极厨具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold the ultimate cooking utensil--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄金锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the golden spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快看上面写的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, look what it says here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众多人试图从这远古肥油中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Many have tried to pull this spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拔出这把锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from this ancient grease
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却无功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all have failed
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有配得上海神王本人的煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Only a fry cook worthy of King Neptune himself
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.93,0:12:32.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:32.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can wield
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄金锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The golden spatula"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我跟黄金锅铲合个影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a picture of me and the spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道菜单区在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you know where the menu section is?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菜单区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The menu section?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这简单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's over that way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy smokes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rude
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯光变暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The light changed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.13,0:13:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.97,0:13:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快拍到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.68,0:13:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能有人配得上皇家厨师的称号了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,someone worthy of being the royal fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.14,0:13:18.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁从肥油里拔出锅铲的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:18.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who has freed the spatula from the grease?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  海神王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did, Mr. Neptune, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是天大的笑话  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A fine jest, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只是个卑贱的黄色海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are but a lowly yellow sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puny
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无足轻重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,insignificant
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平平无奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a commoner
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.42,0:13:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此  你无法成为神的煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you could never be fry cook to a god and
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以才会成为笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is why it is funny
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now step aside
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要寻找真正的煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I seek out the true fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.10,0:13:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你太矮了  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're too short, no
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(658.916,844)}热狗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美味佳肴的提供者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A purveyor of foods
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.86,0:14:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定是我的新任煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you must be my new fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, King Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不负责做  我只负责卖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't make them, I just sell them
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是谁把锅铲拔出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then who pulled up the spatula?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he did
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这笑话听第二次更好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is even funnier a second time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, there--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.00,0:14:20.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甲壳动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:20.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,crustacean
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.96,0:14:21.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁  我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:21.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有着擎天神阿特拉斯的体格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have the physique of Atlas
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我经常健身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I work out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我摆姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make poses with me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碰身子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Body slam
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你把锅铲从肥油里拔出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You pulled the spatula from the grease
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我  是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, that was SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩笑开得过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This joke has gone far enough
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的煎炸厨师在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my fry cook?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有着如此肥硕身躯的你  想必知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Certainly you with your prodigious girth would know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁能做出符合皇家口味的汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who can flip a burger to suit a royal palate
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非得要我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I expected to believe
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.75,0:15:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个生物就是皇家煎炸厨师的人选吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this creature is royal fry cook material?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你没有任何证据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you have any proof
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西给本王擦尾鳍都不配
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This thing is unfit to even scrub the royal tail fin
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.97,0:15:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且  从油锅里拔出锅铲还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And besides, it's not just enough
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to pull a spatula off a greasy griddle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there are certain
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要有指定的特点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,qualities that a royal fry cook must have
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇家煎炸厨师必须是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The royal fry cook must be
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,左撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,left-handed
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我两只都是左手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've got two
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且皇家煎炸厨师穿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Also, the royal fry cook wears
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红色内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the red underwear
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, blue
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇家煎炸厨师的钱包里有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The royal fry cook's wallet contains
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的大脚趾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,his big toes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有六个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He has six
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是新任皇家煎炸厨师  你得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is the new royal fry cook and you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silence
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面是不是很热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it hot in here, or what?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.84,0:15:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你伤到我朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hurt my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你根本就算不上王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not a king
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是个恶霸跟骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a bully and a liar
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, little one
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自以为拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think you have
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成为我煎炸厨师的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what it takes to be my fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会证明你有多么一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will prove your worthlessness
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要通过一项考验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shall be tested with a challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝什么考验都能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob can handle any
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.29,0:16:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你朋友的傲慢将让你付出惨痛代价
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your friend's arrogance will cost you dearly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要通过两项考验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There will be two challenges
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才两项
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only two?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两项考验哪难得倒海绵宝宝这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are two challenges to someone like SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三项考验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three challenges
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三项
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三项考验根本没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three challenges are nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码五百项考验还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Might as well be 500 challenges
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,将就一项好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll settle for one
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.56,0:16:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一项考验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There will be but one challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.69,0:16:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要跟我对决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will face me in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终极厨艺擂台赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the ultimate cook-off
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.91,0:17:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先修好我朋友再接受你考验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:17:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will accept your challenge if you fix my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圆家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the round one
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会复原他的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall restore him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How you feeling?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty good
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, have you gotten taller?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你未来可能的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,see the fate that may lie ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为  假如有很小的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For, if by some minute chance
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功迎接了考验
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you meet the challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么你将会得到丰厚的奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your reward will be great
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Woopsie
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在请看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now behold--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:38.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476.663,112)}来自亚特兰蒂斯的问候
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.95,0:17:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我挚爱的家  亚特兰蒂斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my beloved home of Atlantis
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,堪比太阳神阿波罗的奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A prize worthy of Apollo
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你将定居于此神圣之地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will reside here in this glorious place
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只为我下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cook only for me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and be a god
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds pretty good
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是如果你没有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if you should not succeed
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须放弃煎炸厨师工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you must give up fry cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,forever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very well, then
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往海神波塞殿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the Poseidome
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702.978,386)}海神波塞殿
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到终极厨艺擂台赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,welcome to the ultimate cook-off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  先做出一千个汉堡的人获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, mates first to a thousand patties wins
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shake hands
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿最强者获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May the best man win
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回到各自的场角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go back to your corners
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铃声一响  开始下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when the bell sounds, come out cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对你充满信心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have total confidence in you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(586.816,220)}赌局
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全押海神王赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put it all on Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.54,0:18:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这水平还不配
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not good enough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去亚特兰蒂斯下厨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to cook in Atlantis, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不该接受这项考验
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never should have taken the challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.55,0:18:40.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别放弃你的梦想  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:40.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't give up your dream, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别人曾经跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People used to tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你一点出息都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Patrick, you'll never amount to anything
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你老是异想天开  眼高手低
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll always have your head in the clouds"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在看看我  眼低手高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But just look at me now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get 'em, tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:09.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(500.696,922)}面包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(404.562,328)}海神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(919.278,292)}客队
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Once upon a time"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手下败将
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费汉堡大家有份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free patties for everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fools
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是没味蕾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you no taste buds?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些根本没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with these
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼不敢吃自己做的汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too chicken to eat his own burger
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you eat it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己尝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.39,0:20:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我汉堡不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, mine's no good
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你们凭什么会觉得他的会比我好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what makes you think his will be any better?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, it tastes so good
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想再吃一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'd like to try it a second time
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.04,0:21:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.75,0:21:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的汉堡更好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yours is superior
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此  我向你承认
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I concede to you--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.59,0:21:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants, you win
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去亚特兰蒂斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to Atlantis
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去亚特兰蒂斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to Atlantis
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.06,0:21:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要让那个讨厌的东西进宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That repulsive thing in my palace?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.40,0:21:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说派大星不能跟着来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean Patrick can't come?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的小子  你唯一需要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only friend you'll need, my dear boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是皇家烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the royal grill
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.87,0:21:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴认识你  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was nice knowing you, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也会想你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll miss you, too
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都赌输了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost me bet
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.01,0:22:06.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿好行李
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:06.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,grab your things
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候启程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to depart
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往亚特兰蒂斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to Atlantis
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.81,0:22:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.47,0:22:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.14,0:22:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too late now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.52,0:22:23.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有你的汉堡我无法生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:23.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't live without your burgers
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你将成为神  喜欢上神的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to be a god and like it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.78,0:22:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能的确是有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we do have a problem
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.95,0:22:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着  海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有另外一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have another idea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242.337,322)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  蟹堡王的员工们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Krusty crew
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.55,0:22:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想来点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'll you have?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.72,0:22:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能先失陪一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you excuse me?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.72,0:22:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死的炉子烫到了我的手指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The accursed stove has burnt my finger
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受你自己的怒火吧  炉子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel thine own wrath, stove
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.27,0:22:58.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是怎么跟你交代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:22:58.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使用法力的事呢  实习生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about using your powers, trainee?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.36,0:23:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美的汉堡是用爱做的  不是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect patties are made with love, not magic
